                    "value": "<p>Although a basidirond is immune to cold damage, any effect that deals cold damage causes it to become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed} 1 for [[/r 1d4]] rounds. During this time, it cannot use its Hallucinogenic Cloud or basidirond spores.</p>"
