        },
        {
            "_id": "3GOGRqIhDzmef7he",
            "data": {
                "actionCategory": {
                    "value": "offensive"
                },
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": "2"
                },
                "description": {
                    "chat": "",
                    "unidentified": "",
                    "value": "<p>The basidirond releases a cloud of invisible spores in a 20-foot emanation. Each creature in the area must succeed at a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"22\" data-pf2-traits=\"incapacitation,mental,poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Hallucinogenic Cloud DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save or experience powerful hallucinations as long as it remains in the cloud, plus an additional [[/r 1d4 #rounds]] rounds after leaving the area. A creature must attempt a new save each round it remains within the area. The cloud persists for 5 rounds unless dispersed before then by a strong wind. Each hallucinating creature rolls [[/r 1d6]] each round to determine what it hallucinates that round.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The target is sinking in quicksand. It falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone} and spends 1 action on its next turn flailing its limbs as if attempting to swim.</li>\n<li>The target is attacked by a swarm of spiders. It spends 2 actions on its next turn attacking the floor with a melee weapon (drawing a weapon if needed). It is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} against all attacks.</li>\n<li>An item the target is holding turns into a viper. The target @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Release]{Release} the item and spends its next turn fleeing from it.</li>\n<li>The target is suffocating. It holds its breath and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 3}.</li>\n<li>The target shrinks to 1/10 its normal size. For 1 round it is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 4}, and takes a -10-foot status penalty to its Speed.</li>\n<li>The target is melting. It drops everything it's holding and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 4} for 1 round.</li>\n</ol>"
                },
